title: Help with launcher please :(
body:
Hello, 

I took a few weeks off from LoL coming back recently I open the game.. click Launch.. makes the usual sound but nothing opens. I've tried repairing, trolled the forums for solutions and nothing has helped. I'm here because other than a complete wipe and re-install I'm not sure what I can do.

Anybody have any ideas? 

All help is greatly appreciated.

replies.body:
Bumps do not work on the board. Do with that what you will.

Have you tried running it in admin mode?

If that doesn't work, could you please tell me your ISP and OS?

hey man what exactly is the issue?
{{champion:106}}
Hey, when I click Play League of Legends the Launch screen opens up.. but when I hit launch nothing happens.. So I cant login.
